\rho \cdot C \cdot \dfrac{\partial T}{\partial \tau} + u \cdot \rho \cdot C \cdot \dfrac{\partial T}{\partial r} = \dfrac{\lambda}{r^{2}} \cdot \dfrac{\partial}{\partial r}\left(r^{2} \cdot \dfrac{\partial T}{\partial r}\right) + K - \dfrac{\rho \cdot C \cdot T}{V} \cdot \dfrac{\partial V}{\partial \tau}
