u
V
T_{\tau = 0} = T_{0} \hspace{2cm} 0 \leq r \leq R 
\dfrac{\partial T}{\partial r}\bigg|_{r=0} = 0
\dfrac{\partial T}{\partial r}\bigg|_{r=R} = C1 \cdot (T_{m} - T_{R})
